  "detailed_description": "<h1>The Rewinder Series</h1><p></p><br><h1>Join Our Discord!</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2915490/extras/991a320e12b083b9180b1411c9447bc0.avif?t=1751351456\" width=616 height=196 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Get more information about The Rewinder Series NOW!</strong></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>The Rewinder 2 is an action adventure game inspried by eastern methology. As the last known rewinder, you'll wield the powers of Sizhi god to explore disrrupted villages, dungeons and save people from their dreams. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2915490/extras/eeb2e6a450bac3b166cf4bac47db9124.poster.avif?t=1751351456\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2915490/extras/eeb2e6a450bac3b166cf4bac47db9124.webm?t=1751351456\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2915490/extras/eeb2e6a450bac3b166cf4bac47db9124.mp4?t=1751351456\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2915490/extras/d2e9623d99186937f2263be3dbb97926.webp?t=1751351456\" width=600 height=50 /></span><br>Explore our unique memory levels and puzzles. As the last known rewinder, use your ability to explore others' memory. Bring them out of nightmares. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2915490/extras/0974506eb4772748906c3d9782f0ac26.poster.avif?t=1751351456\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2915490/extras/0974506eb4772748906c3d9782f0ac26.webm?t=1751351456\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2915490/extras/0974506eb4772748906c3d9782f0ac26.mp4?t=1751351456\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2915490/extras/c504276cc3a0516e15bc877c5dd14091.webp?t=1751351456\" width=600 height=50 /></span><br>A unique set of dungeons are waiting for you to explore. Collect different charms to get various bonuses and special abilities.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2915490/extras/e84b5886618662888580b8da0ef08fa3.poster.avif?t=1751351456\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2915490/extras/e84b5886618662888580b8da0ef08fa3.webm?t=1751351456\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2915490/extras/e84b5886618662888580b8da0ef08fa3.mp4?t=1751351456\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2915490/extras/c2b55c89f72267a415307c4270c1b038.webp?t=1751351456\" width=600 height=50 /></span><br>Through out your journey, you will meet all sorts of monsters and ghosts, hear their stories and be friends with them.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2915490/extras/9a2569d43fc41ae4b51b122645ad8b7b.avif?t=1751351456\" width=600 height=338 /></span>",
